		<!-- 📝 Description and Documentation -->
		<summary>A lightweight Webex Interact SMS API client for .NET 8 and later.</summary>
		<description>
			Lightweight C# client for sending SMS messages via the Webex Interact API.
			This library allows easy integration of SMS alerts and notifications into your .NET applications
			using async HTTP requests.
		</description>
		<releaseNotes>
			v1.0.10 - Fixed untracked sources.
			v1.0.9 - Extended releaseNotes, Optimised summary and tags, Verified icon + readme setup, Explicit language + serviceable, XML docs included.
